entirely un-extraordinary.

06:37.898 --> 06:39.638
Right. Don't stand out
in any way.

06:39.733 --> 06:40.722
Exactly.

06:40.818 --> 06:43.184
Don't raise
your hand in class,

06:43.279 --> 06:45.861
and don't even think
about trying out
for cheerleading.

06:45.948 --> 06:48.064
Oh come on, Dad.
