in the world is
one or the other.

13:50.205 --> 13:52.867
Robots do what they're told.
Stick with the herd.

13:52.958 --> 13:56.041
Aliens, on the other hand,
do their own thing.

13:56.753 --> 14:00.041
Well, I don't know.
Do I have to choose?

14:00.882 --> 14:02.418
