give us a second?

16:16.935 --> 16:18.220
Sure.

16:22.107 --> 16:23.187
Is everything okay?

16:23.275 --> 16:25.766
Yeah. I'm just
a little concerned,
that's all.

16:25.902 --> 16:28.735
Molly's been falling
asleep in class
the last week or so.

16:28.822 --> 16:31.985
When I asked her about it,
she said she's been
having some nightmares.

16:33.577 --> 16:35.488
She's got kind of
a big imagination,

16:35.579 --> 16:38.412
and I realize that
there's really nothing
I can do about them,

16:38.498 --> 16:40.739
so I'm just trying to make her
feel as safe as possible.

16:40.834 --> 16:44.747
About that. I know
it's not exactly my place,

16:45.881 --> 16:48.714
