loved and well cared for

16:59.519 --> 17:00.929
and she's doing great.

17:01.021 --> 17:02.807
She's struggling, Mr. Parkman.

17:02.898 --> 17:05.264
Why? Why, because she's
having a few nightmares?

17:05.358 --> 17:07.269
