your brother,

19:46.603 --> 19:48.969
drove Heidi away,
drove your kids away.

19:49.064 --> 19:52.022
If you'd followed our plan,
if you'd done what
you were supposed to,

19:52.108 --> 19:53.973
he would be alive now.

19:54.069 --> 19:56.481
To think I almost
listened to you.

19:59.282 --> 20:00.863
