22:43.446 --> 22:44.902
I'm gonna do it
this morning.

22:44.989 --> 22:46.365
Uh-huh.

22:46.449 --> 22:50.158
And if I wasn't here
watching your every move?

22:51.246 --> 22:52.827
You know, you've been here
for a few months, Butler,

22:52.914 --> 22:55.951
I think it's time I saw
some commitment to
excellence from you.

22:56.042 --> 22:57.703
When I was assistant manager,

22:57.794 --> 23:01.127
we were fully set before
the first customer walked
through that door.

23:01.214 --> 23:03.626
That is how I got this.

23:05.635 --> 23:08.297
Paper business
is dog-eat-dog.

23:09.055 --> 23:10.636
You gotta live it
and breathe it.

23:10.723 --> 23:13.214
You gotta want it.
Do you want it, Butler?

23:15.186 --> 23:16.471
Do you?

23:18.982 --> 23:20.313
Yes, sir.

23:21.484 --> 23:22.644
Yeah.

23:23.736 --> 23:24.942
Well,

23:25.780 --> 23:27.020
we'll see.

23:27.115 --> 23:32.075
The Company was formed
30 years ago with a group
of like-minded individuals.

23:32.161 --> 23:36.370
Ordinary men and women
who were gifted
with extraordinary powers.

23:37.166 --> 23:39.748
They wanted to
help their own.

23:39.836 --> 23:42.703
To find them,
and to protect them.

23:43.548 --> 23:47.632
We find people and we
make sure they don't
become dangerous.

23:48.177 --> 23:50.884
Now, sometimes
that can mean
making sure

23:50.972 --> 23:53.930
they understand entirely
what they're capable of

23:54.017 --> 23:58.181
and teaching them to use
their abilities for the good
of mankind.

23:58.271 --> 24:02.514
And sometimes
it can mean
eliminating them.

24:03.192 --> 24:05.774
Who the hell are you to judge
who lives and who dies?

24:05.862 --> 24:10.071
If I'm not mistaken,
you yourself tried to
put a bullet in the brain

24:10.158 --> 24:11.568
of a man named Sylar.

24:11.659 --> 24:12.774
He was a monster.

24:12.869 --> 24:17.533
Yes, and you were
willing to kill him
for the greater good.

24:17.624 --> 24:22.618
