out of people's minds,
it's unfair.

26:19.203 --> 26:21.740
No. It is my natural talent.

26:21.831 --> 26:23.241
You wouldn't think
a baseball player
is cheating

26:23.332 --> 26:24.742
because he's athletic,
would you?

26:24.834 --> 26:26.825
