and you know it.

26:26.919 --> 26:27.954
No.

26:30.006 --> 26:33.464
You know what? Iwant to talk
to you about these drawings
that you made at school.

26:33.551 --> 26:35.257
You're changing the subject.

26:35.344 --> 26:37.756
Miss Gerber is concerned,
and so am I.

26:37.847 --> 26:41.431
You don't wanna talk
about your exams. I don't
want to talk about my dreams.

26:41.517 --> 26:44.475
Molly, I want to help you.

26:44.562 --> 26:45.722
I don't want you
to be afraid.

26:45.813 --> 26:47.974
