one of us sent these?

39:44.633 --> 39:45.713
Yes.

39:46.176 --> 39:49.794
For the pain we caused.
The people we have killed.

39:51.390 --> 39:53.802
There is no end
to our suffering.

39:54.977 --> 39:59.391
I sought redemption
by helping Hiro

39:59.481 --> 40:02.223
fulfill his destiny
to save the world.

40:04.486 --> 40:06.898
How did you
help your son?

40:11.868 --> 40:13.074
Angela,

40:14.246 --> 40:16.658
I am leaving
for Japan tonight.

40:17.165 --> 40:20.453
