you disappear
as well.

40:31.513 --> 40:33.253
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

40:33.348 --> 40:35.054
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

40:44.568 --> 40:46.775
Oh, no, I broke history!

40:46.862 --> 40:47.897
Villages burn.

40:48.905 --> 40:50.281
Those things happen.

40:50.365 --> 40:51.821
But not like this!

40:52.659 --> 40:55.571
The future may
not exist
as I know it.

40:55.662 --> 40:58.779
No future,
no cars, no Andos.
No me!

40:59.249 --> 41:00.364
Great Scot!

41:00.459 --> 41:05.453
You mustn't fret everything,
my very strange little friend.

41:06.340 --> 41:08.626
Here, have some sake,
it'll brighten your day.

41:08.717 --> 41:10.332
No. Forget sake.

41:10.427 --> 41:12.793
You are supposed
to be a hero.

41:12.888 --> 41:16.176
Being a hero
never filled anyone's sack
with salt and saffron.

41:16.266 --> 41:18.006
It's a waste of time.

41:20.729 --> 41:25.268
In the stories you
are rewarded with more
gold than the Emperor.

41:25.359 --> 41:30.023
And you took the swordsmith's
daughter, the most beautiful
woman in all Japan,

41:30.113 --> 41:31.819
for your princess.

41:33.075 --> 41:34.736
(EXCLAIMS IN PAIN)

41:34.993 --> 41:36.984
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

41:45.420 --> 41:47.502
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

42:00.018 --> 42:02.475
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

